On this page
Set action output to variable's value
This will set the action's output, which can be retrieved via Set Variable to Last Output after this action executes, to the value of the given variable. This is necessary if you want to return an entity or object like NPCs, Game Objects, etc.
note
Make sure to call this BEFORE returning true or false if you choose to use one of those.

Variable name (text)
